OL,3,CThree dead and three arrested after
OL,4,Ccar crash
OL,6,FThree young men have died after a car
OL,7,Fcrash in Halifax.
OL,9,FPolice were called to Keighley Road,
OL,10,FIllingworth, at 6.50pm on Wednesday
OL,11,Fafter a collision between a Ford
OL,12,FFiesta, a BMW and a Renault Clio.
OL,14,FTwo men aged 22 and a 21-year-old, who
OL,15,Fwere in the Fiesta, died at the scene.
OL,17,FA 21-year-old man who was also in the
OL,18,Fcar was taken to hospital with life-
OL,19,Fthreatening injuries.
