OL,3,CThree dead and three arrested after
OL,4,Ccar crash
OL,6,FA 37-year-old man and two women aged
OL,7,F18 and 32, all from Halifax, who were
OL,8,Fin the BMW, have been arrested on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,10,Fdangerous driving.
OL,12,FThe Clio was stationary and unoccupied
OL,13,Fat the time of the collision.
OL,15,FThe road remained closed on Thursday
OL,16,Fwhile enquiries were carried out.
OL,18,FDet Sgt Paul Lightowler, of the West
OL,19,FYorkshire Police Major Collision
OL,20,FEnquiry Team, appealed for witnesses
OL,21,Fto come forward.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
