OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1773947499
OL,3,CThree dead and three arrested after
OL,4,Ccar crash
OL,6,FHe said: "Our thoughts go out to the
OL,7,Ffamily and friends of the people who
OL,8,Fdied. Specially trained officers will
OL,9,Fbe supporting the families involved.
OL,11,F"This is a tragic incident and
OL,12,Fextensive enquiries are ongoing at the
OL,13,Fscene this morning."
